The term '''microphysics''' refers to areas of physics that study phenomena that take place on the [[microscopic scale]] (length scales smaller than 1 mm), such as:
* [[Atomic physics]] * [[Cloud physics]] * [[Mesoscopic physics]] * [[Molecular physics]] * [[Nanotechnology]] * [[Nuclear physics]] * [[Particle physics]] * [[Plasma physics]] * [[Quantum mechanics]] * [[String theory]]
